    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<p>Bolverkt is a Djúpdvergr (deep-dwelling dwarf-kin) scout stationed near the Steam-Oasis. She is compact, umber-dark of skin, and economical with words. She serves as first contact for any heroes who investigate the ledge-watcher above the oasis path. If the party chooses to follow, she leads them to Djúphól and the optional Heitfolk side quest. She also serves as guide through the Heitfolk tunnels if the party completes Hildvarðâ€™s task.</p>",
        "public": ""
